          <title>Swipe my Alfred Workflow for Drafts for Mac</title>
          <dc:creator><![CDATA[handythinks]]></dc:creator>
          <category>Drafts for Mac</category>
          <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Hi y’all. I created an Alfred workflow to help interact with Drafts for Mac quickly.</p>
<p>Here is <a href="https://www.evernote.com/l/AAUhw9bg9TRHAYbKJOWYqumA8CBJElMdw1A" rel="nofollow noopener">a link to download</a> it.</p>
<p></p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/original/2X/0/0ef067d0c5db311ddc05be771f55cf537ded8221.png" data-download-href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/0ef067d0c5db311ddc05be771f55cf537ded8221" title="Screen Shot 2019-03-08 at 1.17.18 PM.png"><img src="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/0/0ef067d0c5db311ddc05be771f55cf537ded8221_2_690x306.png" alt="18%20PM" width="690" height="306" srcset="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/0/0ef067d0c5db311ddc05be771f55cf537ded8221_2_690x306.png, https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/0/0ef067d0c5db311ddc05be771f55cf537ded8221_2_1035x459.png 1.5x, https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/original/2X/0/0ef067d0c5db311ddc05be771f55cf537ded8221.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/0/0ef067d0c5db311ddc05be771f55cf537ded8221_2_10x10.png"></a></div><p></p>
<p>It incorporated a menu that can be called upon by using “d” space. A quick keyword trigger is also available for each one.</p>
<p>It supports:</p>
<ol>
<li>Create New Draft (<strong>dd</strong>)</li>
<li>Search Drafts (<strong>ds</strong>)</li>
<li>Prepend a set Draft (<strong>dp</strong>)</li>
<li>Append a set Draft (<strong>da</strong>)</li>
</ol>
<p>3 and 4 require setup in the workflow tool. See end of post for this.</p>
<h2>Menu Driven Actions</h2>
<p>type “d” space and then you’ll get these actions, select one and press enter. Let’s create a new draft.<br>
</p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/original/2X/2/2d6ff7a4bf08ea1fff3451aaec014df816b5c648.png" data-download-href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/2d6ff7a4bf08ea1fff3451aaec014df816b5c648" title="Screen Shot 2019-03-08 at 1.31.19 PM.png"><img src="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/2d6ff7a4bf08ea1fff3451aaec014df816b5c648_2_690x317.png" alt="19%20PM" width="690" height="317" srcset="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/2d6ff7a4bf08ea1fff3451aaec014df816b5c648_2_690x317.png, https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/2d6ff7a4bf08ea1fff3451aaec014df816b5c648_2_1035x475.png 1.5x, https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/original/2X/2/2d6ff7a4bf08ea1fff3451aaec014df816b5c648.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/2d6ff7a4bf08ea1fff3451aaec014df816b5c648_2_10x10.png"></a></div><br>
type your draft and press enter<br>
<div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/original/2X/0/029fece9fdaedf293d689c1b6516aceb6ae10617.png" data-download-href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/029fece9fdaedf293d689c1b6516aceb6ae10617" title="Screen Shot 2019-03-08 at 1.31.49 PM.png"><img src="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/0/029fece9fdaedf293d689c1b6516aceb6ae10617_2_690x145.png" alt="49%20PM" width="690" height="145" srcset="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/0/029fece9fdaedf293d689c1b6516aceb6ae10617_2_690x145.png, https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/0/029fece9fdaedf293d689c1b6516aceb6ae10617_2_1035x217.png 1.5x, https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/original/2X/0/029fece9fdaedf293d689c1b6516aceb6ae10617.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/0/029fece9fdaedf293d689c1b6516aceb6ae10617_2_10x10.png"></a></div><br>
notification will tell you it was successful<br>
<div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/original/2X/9/9ef1756585be161dfec73a7ede43ee1638979f68.png" data-download-href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/9ef1756585be161dfec73a7ede43ee1638979f68" title="Screen Shot 2019-03-08 at 1.31.55 PM.png"><img src="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/9/9ef1756585be161dfec73a7ede43ee1638979f68_2_690x168.png" alt="55%20PM" width="690" height="168" srcset="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/9/9ef1756585be161dfec73a7ede43ee1638979f68_2_690x168.png, https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/original/2X/9/9ef1756585be161dfec73a7ede43ee1638979f68.png 1.5x, https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/original/2X/9/9ef1756585be161dfec73a7ede43ee1638979f68.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/9/9ef1756585be161dfec73a7ede43ee1638979f68_2_10x10.png"></a></div><br>
and here it is!<br>
<img src="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/original/2X/b/b792c06c59659a39c4be89371461673ae78fad6b.png" alt="04%20PM" width="586" height="134"><p></p>
<h2>Quick Actions</h2>
<p><strong>New Draft</strong><br>
Call it up with it’s quick keyword.<br>
</p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/original/2X/2/2050836bc47db0fb8b202daab552400344988b2f.png" data-download-href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/2050836bc47db0fb8b202daab552400344988b2f" title="Screen Shot 2019-03-08 at 1.18.04 PM.png"><img src="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/2050836bc47db0fb8b202daab552400344988b2f_2_690x142.png" alt="04%20PM" width="690" height="142" srcset="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/2050836bc47db0fb8b202daab552400344988b2f_2_690x142.png, https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/2050836bc47db0fb8b202daab552400344988b2f_2_1035x213.png 1.5x, https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/original/2X/2/2050836bc47db0fb8b202daab552400344988b2f.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/2/2050836bc47db0fb8b202daab552400344988b2f_2_10x10.png"></a></div><p></p>
<p>Then keep typing to enter text and press enter.<br>
</p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/original/2X/5/5a9218a53f85391a426e3667e3514c3b7dcebd8e.png" data-download-href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/5a9218a53f85391a426e3667e3514c3b7dcebd8e" title="Screen Shot 2019-03-08 at 1.20.07 PM.png"><img src="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/5/5a9218a53f85391a426e3667e3514c3b7dcebd8e_2_690x151.png" alt="07%20PM" width="690" height="151" srcset="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/5/5a9218a53f85391a426e3667e3514c3b7dcebd8e_2_690x151.png, https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/5/5a9218a53f85391a426e3667e3514c3b7dcebd8e_2_1035x226.png 1.5x, https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/original/2X/5/5a9218a53f85391a426e3667e3514c3b7dcebd8e.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/5/5a9218a53f85391a426e3667e3514c3b7dcebd8e_2_10x10.png"></a></div><p></p>
<p>You’ll get a notification that the draft was made.<br>
</p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/original/2X/7/70b258c8cec68299b454bde088c3e2b265329d58.png" data-download-href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/70b258c8cec68299b454bde088c3e2b265329d58" title="Screen Shot 2019-03-08 at 1.20.12 PM.png"><img src="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/70b258c8cec68299b454bde088c3e2b265329d58_2_690x140.png" alt="12%20PM" width="690" height="140" srcset="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/70b258c8cec68299b454bde088c3e2b265329d58_2_690x140.png, https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/original/2X/7/70b258c8cec68299b454bde088c3e2b265329d58.png 1.5x, https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/original/2X/7/70b258c8cec68299b454bde088c3e2b265329d58.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/7/70b258c8cec68299b454bde088c3e2b265329d58_2_10x10.png"></a></div><br>
And sure enough, here it is.<br>
<img src="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/original/2X/7/75fd5e48d3a81d6d8801b4cca8f8238393f073b5.png" alt="26%20PM" width="594" height="152"><p></p>
<p><strong>Search</strong><br>
Search is super easy. Just type “ds <em>your search here</em>” and press enter.<br>
</p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/original/2X/c/ca1ce08b6425350473cad252fa7f284a8ab50768.png" data-download-href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/ca1ce08b6425350473cad252fa7f284a8ab50768" title="Screen Shot 2019-03-08 at 1.40.00 PM.png"><img src="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/ca1ce08b6425350473cad252fa7f284a8ab50768_2_690x146.png" alt="00%20PM" width="690" height="146" srcset="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/ca1ce08b6425350473cad252fa7f284a8ab50768_2_690x146.png, https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/ca1ce08b6425350473cad252fa7f284a8ab50768_2_1035x219.png 1.5x, https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/original/2X/c/ca1ce08b6425350473cad252fa7f284a8ab50768.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/c/ca1ce08b6425350473cad252fa7f284a8ab50768_2_10x10.png"></a></div><br>
This one is probably my favorite because it’s so quick. It just pulls up the search.<br>
<img src="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/original/2X/d/d77a21acfc29f6bfabe002be4766e499b3012f86.png" alt="14%20PM" width="572" height="390"><p></p>
<h2>Back End View</h2>
<p></p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/original/2X/6/683dd7dcced8eaac166db49eb6f78e467c0b933b.png" data-download-href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/683dd7dcced8eaac166db49eb6f78e467c0b933b" title="Screen Shot 2019-03-08 at 1.14.08 PM 1.png"><img src="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/6/683dd7dcced8eaac166db49eb6f78e467c0b933b_2_468x500.png" alt="08%20PM%201" width="468" height="500" srcset="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/6/683dd7dcced8eaac166db49eb6f78e467c0b933b_2_468x500.png, https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/6/683dd7dcced8eaac166db49eb6f78e467c0b933b_2_702x750.png 1.5x, https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/6/683dd7dcced8eaac166db49eb6f78e467c0b933b_2_936x1000.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/6/683dd7dcced8eaac166db49eb6f78e467c0b933b_2_10x10.png"></a></div><p></p>
<h3>Prepend/Append Setup</h3>
<p>Find your target note’s UUID like this:<br>
</p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/original/2X/3/302fa40419283f5c521acc87de997b20abb6d4c0.png" data-download-href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/302fa40419283f5c521acc87de997b20abb6d4c0" title="Screen Shot 2019-03-08 at 1.28.39 PM.png"><img src="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/3/302fa40419283f5c521acc87de997b20abb6d4c0_2_468x500.png" alt="39%20PM" width="468" height="500" srcset="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/3/302fa40419283f5c521acc87de997b20abb6d4c0_2_468x500.png, https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/original/2X/3/302fa40419283f5c521acc87de997b20abb6d4c0.png 1.5x, https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/original/2X/3/302fa40419283f5c521acc87de997b20abb6d4c0.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/3/302fa40419283f5c521acc87de997b20abb6d4c0_2_10x10.png"></a></div><p></p>
<p>Then head in here in the workflow:</p>
<p></p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/original/2X/a/acc05d623246b79dde0e32e94a20efb3369e1c4d.png" data-download-href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/acc05d623246b79dde0e32e94a20efb3369e1c4d" title="Screen Shot 2019-03-08 at 1.25.02 PM.png"><img src="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/a/acc05d623246b79dde0e32e94a20efb3369e1c4d_2_690x498.png" alt="02%20PM" width="690" height="498" srcset="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/a/acc05d623246b79dde0e32e94a20efb3369e1c4d_2_690x498.png, https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/a/acc05d623246b79dde0e32e94a20efb3369e1c4d_2_1035x747.png 1.5x, https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/a/acc05d623246b79dde0e32e94a20efb3369e1c4d_2_1380x996.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/a/acc05d623246b79dde0e32e94a20efb3369e1c4d_2_10x10.png"></a></div><p></p>
<p>And replace the highlighted text with the actual UUID.</p>
<p></p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/original/2X/4/40752d1ecd990a55fd00e4ef117ad20f3fd4ee7c.png" data-download-href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/40752d1ecd990a55fd00e4ef117ad20f3fd4ee7c" title="Screen Shot 2019-03-08 at 1.28.16 PM.png"><img src="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/4/40752d1ecd990a55fd00e4ef117ad20f3fd4ee7c_2_690x136.png" alt="16%20PM" width="690" height="136" srcset="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/4/40752d1ecd990a55fd00e4ef117ad20f3fd4ee7c_2_690x136.png, https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/4/40752d1ecd990a55fd00e4ef117ad20f3fd4ee7c_2_1035x204.png 1.5x, https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/original/2X/4/40752d1ecd990a55fd00e4ef117ad20f3fd4ee7c.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/4/40752d1ecd990a55fd00e4ef117ad20f3fd4ee7c_2_10x10.png"></a></div><p></p>
<p>Don’t forget to remove the big text warning.</p>
<p></p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/original/2X/a/acc05d623246b79dde0e32e94a20efb3369e1c4d.png" data-download-href="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/acc05d623246b79dde0e32e94a20efb3369e1c4d" title="Screen Shot 2019-03-08 at 1.25.02 PM.png"><img src="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/a/acc05d623246b79dde0e32e94a20efb3369e1c4d_2_690x498.png" alt="02%20PM" width="690" height="498" srcset="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/a/acc05d623246b79dde0e32e94a20efb3369e1c4d_2_690x498.png, https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/a/acc05d623246b79dde0e32e94a20efb3369e1c4d_2_1035x747.png 1.5x, https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/a/acc05d623246b79dde0e32e94a20efb3369e1c4d_2_1380x996.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://forums.getdrafts.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/a/acc05d623246b79dde0e32e94a20efb3369e1c4d_2_10x10.png"></a></div><p></p>
<p>You should be done!</p>
