          <title>Fantastically Good Event Parser</title>
          <dc:creator><![CDATA[pdavisonreiber]]></dc:creator>
          <category>Actions - Share What You&#39;ve Made</category>
          <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Any fans of Fantastical’s natural language entry for calendar events will like this one. Basically, I have recreated the same functionality in Drafts using JavaScript. Events can be added on multiple lines and then instantly added to the calendar, no pinging back and forth with URL schemes.</p>
<p>More details <a href="https://polymaths.blog/2018/06/fantastically-good-event-parser-for-drafts-5" rel="nofollow noopener">on my blog</a>, and here’s a <a href="https://actions.getdrafts.com/a/1Lk" rel="nofollow noopener">link to the action</a> in the directory.</p>
